{"tid":751689,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【英超】查理阿當插沙基利：史城降班最衰係佢","createTime":"2018-07-22T06:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T11:59:12.000Z","uid":161311,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d392af9a671ccb82b871928ccd664e443c50cda4","tid":751689,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"上周落實加盟利物浦的梳頓沙基利，遭前史篤城隊友兼紅軍舊將查理阿當怒插名不符實。<br />\n<br />\n查理阿當對於這位剛由1,350萬鎊轉投利物浦的瑞士球星嗤之以鼻，指史篤城上季遭受降班厄運，主要便是隊內幾名球星未能踢出水準：「當士氣低落，你需要陣中的大牌球員帶來魔力，但這些所謂的大牌，從來沒有帶來好的表現，他（沙基利）當然是其中一位。」<br />\n<br />\n這位在2011/12球季短暫效力紅軍的蘇格蘭中場再補充：「是的，所有人都應該帶來幫助，但對於球會某些管理人員，卻經常稱讚那些大牌球員，但他們卻沒有表現出來，甚至無事生產。不過，大家聽著，他已經走了，我們會繼續前進，未來目標就是在英冠爭取升班。」<br />\n<br />\n沙基利上季在史篤城踢了36場聯賽，射入8球，包括在尾2一輪對水晶宮的關鍵比賽，曾入球先開紀錄，可惜球隊最後反勝為敗，以1:2敗陣，落實今季要落英冠作賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58463902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58463902&d=gjMC5PI8QlnGZQbbeUTcee9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=29f61337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58463902&h=86376a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58463902</a>"},{"pid":"fe1daf155cb723c92154c5d935e5f92b1df493df","tid":751689,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a45e8d2f8abb38adb024846027041bd660615ef","tid":751689,"uid":6497,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"會然沙基利回應下"},{"pid":"3cf64